aiAdjustments.reasoning: Low-key portrait with warm/red spill. To make it mystical and dramatic while keeping professionalism, I open exposure slightly on the subject, deepen blacks, contain highlights, and add cool-blue shadows with warm amber highlights via Color Grading. Vibrance increases subject color richness while overall saturation is restrained to avoid cartoonish tones. HSL targets hair (orange) for glow and pushes reds slightly deeper for mood. Subtle dehaze/clarity/texture refine detail. Vignette and parametric curve add controlled contrast without crushing skin.
